title: Noelani Day
text: Noelani Day (born 24 April 2003) is a Tongan <a href="Swimming%20%28sport%29">swimmer</a>. She competed in the <a href="Swimming%20at%20the%202019%20World%20Aquatics%20Championships%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%2050%20metre%20freestyle">women's 50 metre freestyle</a> at the <a href="2019%20World%20Aquatics%20Championships">2019 World Aquatics Championships</a> and she finished in 67th place. In 2021, she competed in the <a href="Swimming%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%2050%20metre%20freestyle">women's 50 metre freestyle</a> event at the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics">2020 Summer Olympics</a> held in Tokyo, Japan.
